            "heading": "Making patterns readable",
            "heading_tag": "h3",
            "text": "<p>Processed data is translated into clear visual outputs, including graphs, diagrams, and comparative views.<br/></p><p>These visuals help identify balance, stress distribution, and systemic relationships in an accessible format.</p>",
