          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Common professional applications include:</strong></p><ul><li>Conducting individual energy assessments during sessions</li><li>Supporting practitioner–client dialogue through visual data</li><li>Comparing measurements before and after sessions or interventions</li><li>Monitoring functional balance and stress-related dynamics over time</li><li>Documenting follow-up processes in professional practice</li><li>Supporting educational or research-oriented observation workflows</li></ul>",
