        "columns_mobile": "1",
        "swipe_on_mobile": true,
        "heading": "A Structured Foundation for Energy Observation",
        "heading_size": "title-xl tracking-heading",
        "heading_alignment": "text-center md:items-center",
        "heading_tag": "h2",
        "subheading": "",
        "description": "<p>Bio-Well 3.0 is designed to support structured observation, visual analysis, and professional follow-up through electro-photonic imaging.<br/><br/>By providing consistent measurements and clear visual representations, it offers practitioners a reliable framework to contextualize functional energy dynamics, compare results over time, and document their analytical work with precision.<br/><br/>Bio-Well 3.0 does not diagnose or treat.<br/>It functions as an analytical observation system, supporting professional interpretation, educational exploration, and research-oriented practices within an ethical and clearly defined scope.</p>",
